              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"appointmentStatus\": \"CHECKED_IN\",\n  \"remark\": \"患者已到院签到\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "## 2.5.6 更新就诊状态\n\n**状态流转**：\n- BOOKED → CHECKED_IN（签到）\n- CHECKED_IN → IN_PROGRESS（叫号就诊）\n- IN_PROGRESS → COMPLETED（就诊完成）\n- BOOKED/CHECKED_IN → NO_SHOW（爽约/过号）\n- CANCELLED 是终态，不可跳转\n\n**需登录**。"
